1829
01:24:26,253 --> 01:24:29,047
<i>about what the context of the movie is.</i>

1830
01:24:29,131 --> 01:24:30,799
<i>It would be impossible
to tell without it.</i>

1831
01:24:30,883 --> 01:24:31,883
HAHN: <i>Yeah.</i>

1832
01:24:31,967 --> 01:24:33,718
MINKOFF: <i>A lot of.. This is really…</i>

1833
01:24:33,802 --> 01:24:35,553
<i>Animated films are about the process</i>

1834
01:24:35,637 --> 01:24:37,263
<i>as much as anything else.</i>

1835
01:24:37,347 --> 01:24:39,641
<i>And there always comes a
