1838
01:24:51,779 --> 01:24:53,823
<i>and you know, there's always a sense of</i>

1839
01:24:53,907 --> 01:24:55,157
<i>is it all that it could be,</i>

1840
01:24:55,241 --> 01:24:57,159
<i>could we have done
something better with it?</i>

1841
01:24:57,243 --> 01:24:58,994
<i>And some pieces, of course, you feel,</i>

1842
01:24:59,078 --> 01:25:00,371
<i>"You know, we succeeded pretty well.</i>"

1843
01:25:00,455 --> 01:25:01,705
<i>And of course, there's
other pieces where you say,</i>

1844
01:25:01,789 --> 01:25:03,374
<i>"You know, maybe we
could have gone for it.</i>"

1845
01:25:03,458 --> 01:25:04,792
HAHN: <i>It's tough.
