<i>another was done in Los Angeles,</i>

1888
01:27:00,828 --> 01:27:02,537
<i>the chorus was recorded in London,</i>

1889
01:27:02,621 --> 01:27:04,623
<i>and the music was done in Santa Monica.</i>

1890
01:27:04,707 --> 01:27:06,458
<i>You know, it's spread
out all over the place,</i>

1891
01:27:06,542 --> 01:27:09,336
<i>and somehow that all
comes together into one piece.</i>

1892
01:27:09,420 --> 01:27:11,880
-MINKOFF: <i>It's the magic of animation.</i>
-HAHN: <i>It is magical.</i>

1893
01:27:11,964 --> 01:27:14,841
MINKOFF: <i>In fact, one of the big
